the code of the repository https://github.com/tobiashuste/amgx-c-wrapper.git
must be downloaded in this folder, getting the following tree :

shyfem
└─── amgx-c-wrapper
     ├─── meson.build
     ├─── README_shyfem
     └─── amgx-c-wrapper
          ├── LICENSE
          ├── Makefile
          ├── README.md
          └── src
              ├── amgx_c_wrapper.cpp
              └── amgx_c_wrapper.h

(git clone git@github.com:tobiashuste/amgx-c-wrapper.git)
